Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現我的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.73,0:01:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就像是復活一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害啊 面麻居然為了讓你幫她實現願望而回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.28,0:02:05.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…我想應該只是我看到的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.07,0:02:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻覺？那是說魔幻？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好酷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 她現在也在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.15,0:02:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.01,0:02:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 是我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.61,0:02:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這嗎 這裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪啊 面麻 露個臉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一衝動把面麻的事情說了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到他竟然這麼輕易就相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.95,0:02:29.29,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊  我看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.17,0:02:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了只是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳果然厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.60,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個秘密基地是你一直在用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.37,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過僅限我待在日本的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 那些紅色標記 都是我去過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.96,0:02:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想去世界各地看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在用打工賺的錢去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:02:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有時間去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.68,0:03:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久前去了東南亞環遊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越南的女孩超可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.73,0:03:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 好強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前明明是個小不點 居然長成這麼大塊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.37,0:03:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…一點都沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.52,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣這樣這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.31,0:03:19.44,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可愛啊 萌死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變了很多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jungle cruise 會出現什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑題了 跑題了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是說面麻的願望來著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.33,0:03:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做過什麼約定嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.51,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我沒什麼印象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是說過想要仁碳手裡的「Desu Yo.」簽名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:42.24,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Desu Yo.：日本搞笑藝人 本名齊藤哲也
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會為了「Desu Yo.」的簽名特意化成鬼回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是那個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.09,0:04:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 栗丸你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.99,0:04:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家餵你酸奶喝啊 酸奶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.45,0:04:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.16,0:04:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 鳴子 你真的去了宿海的家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然被迫去搭理一個家裡蹲 真夠你受的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.73,0:04:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 偶爾不都會有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不知為啥提不起精神 早上爬不起來之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我偶爾也會…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 經常會
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 但是不想被人跟那種陰暗的傢伙放到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.61,0:04:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在肯定在拿鳴子你幻想一些色色的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:05:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.24,0:05:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王大附高的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.24,0:05:14.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.63,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴…鶴見同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 你忘東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況下你可以不用管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且被誰看到我和綠高的人說話會很丟人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:50.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.15,0:05:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 人家好心幫你拿來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又沒拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.91,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你什麼時候變得這麼跩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一直是怯生生的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:02.25,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！不要不要 別吵 安鳴和鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:04.56,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不許吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一點沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從以前開始就很容易受人影響
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.10,0:06:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和跟你一起的那些貌似胯下輕浮的女人沒兩樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胯下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明以前總是在模仿本間芽衣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要隨便提起死人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己說完自己倒憋屈 真是無可救藥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是你 還是雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鶴子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.32,0:06:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直想要變成面麻那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.67,0:07:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.91,0:07:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 仁碳你…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡面麻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有那樣挑動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.92,0:07:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會喜歡這種醜八怪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 也不會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.89,0:07:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.18,0:08:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙一呱呱 就該回家家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙一呱呱…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻…應該回去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.16,0:08:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您要找什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.33,0:08:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.99,0:08:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？Nokemon？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.42,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捏遊戲POKEMON(PM) 以下簡稱NM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還對客人買的東西有意見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪一版NM 乳白？翠綠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.56,0:08:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.46,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？NM金？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是多少年前出的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 有的話就賣給我 快點賣給我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稀有NM？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對 面麻不是很想要來著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.58,0:09:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就是一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來 她一直念叨什麼「Building Builder」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4,571日元
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年前的遊戲還按定價 真會坑錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你 這可是良心價
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.02,0:09:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經很難搞到了 所以有升值
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.14,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 謝謝光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.45,0:10:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 回來啦 仁太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.96,0:10:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.36,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天現場出了不錯的盤子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以今晚吃烤肉大餐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我沒有食慾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼啊 一點都不可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:16.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼玩來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…首先從三隻中選一隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.54,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻還沒有回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.90,0:10:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的壓力具現成的我的幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就應該是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.75,0:10:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.23,0:11:22.06,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,130)}第2話 勇者面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:22.01,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者面麻發現NM商店
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.06,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.48,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.17,0:11:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波…久川
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.60,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前一樣還叫我波波就行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼見外嘛 小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次被人這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦好啦 對了 雪集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了沒 面麻在仁碳那裡復活了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 到現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.77,0:12:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 宿海怎麼說面麻的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 仁碳啊 好久沒見他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.40,0:12:12.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他還是那麼厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿海怎麼說面麻的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻聽？好像是幻覺什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:27.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不太清楚 但好像是面麻想讓他實現願望
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 不小心睡…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.84,0:12:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻 你回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你洗什麼澡啊 老爸明明還在家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:13:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳 洗身子只覺得涼颼颼的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻討厭那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.83,0:13:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 應該更深刻意識到自己已經發育…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…雖說一部分沒怎麼發育
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一部分？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.48,0:13:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我先穿上衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 好眼熟的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔好 好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 難道是波波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大個 發育期好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波波
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和朋友交換？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 聽說利用連接線 互相交換NM就能得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.51,0:13:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔 肉好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是昨晚剩的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那叔叔我去工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:14:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢…慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.94,0:14:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我給忘光了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 面麻說過要大家一起才能實現
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.14,0:14:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 波波 你怎麼想起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.56,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥 我也看到幻聽了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻聽可不是看的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 那只要再得到一個NM的軟體…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要說誰還有NM…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候 我超級討厭自己的卷毛和眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很羨慕那個擁有飄逸長髮的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被仁太喜歡的面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴 我們弄一樣的貼紙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 這個可愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給安鳴一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.28,0:15:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.28,0:15:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明最喜歡面麻了 卻又很討厭她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.38,0:15:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴子 能不能來一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會使喚人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.25,0:15:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 就是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.62,0:15:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼啊 還要我也玩NM？沒門
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.57,0:15:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾回歸下童心也沒什麼不好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是吧 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.59,0:15:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 眼鏡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.69,0:16:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.65,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.37,0:16:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來 你們倆好久沒過來玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃昨晚鳴子做的果凍嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 安鳴的果凍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼叫
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 稀有NM是面麻的願望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 叫你不要說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…算是她托夢給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻托夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找找 NM的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 那是「Love&Perry」的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是牛魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.98,0:16:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 牛魔王啊 是有這玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.18,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要找牛魔王 是NM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼一直不過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.67,0:16:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為面麻在的話 媽媽和安鳴都會變得很傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:57.76,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是DM
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:16:58.65,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DM啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:16:59.97,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.09,0:17:00.50,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.20,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找NM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:04.36,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NM是吧 對 是NM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:05.37,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在認真找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.47,0:17:07.82,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話 你有沒有認真找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.98,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.91,0:17:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找個地方坐著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Bobobo」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這種小遊戲還寫名字 你還真是一板一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉上嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隔這麼久再看「Bobobo」 覺得好好笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不敢相信 為什麼沒有魔法寶瓶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為稀有NM不是要交換劇毒怪和元氣爆發怪嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野外沒有劇毒怪 必須從魔法寶瓶進化
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:18:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安鳴果然沒有變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是很溫柔 有很多遊戲和漫畫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒有這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.88,0:18:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.69,0:18:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進化出劇毒怪啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.45,0:18:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 安城
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.61,0:19:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 就當作消磨時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.00,0:19:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你有回報嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.22,0:19:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.76,0:19:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來學校上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.21,0:19:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點 剩下的就是把連接線插上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 這樣就可以和朋友交換
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安城？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.58,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請勿中途拔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.58,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通信中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.23,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜！稀有NM友好王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,NM
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到手啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好 仁碳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 這樣面麻也會高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.12,0:20:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望 好像不是這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.88,0:20:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有好多好事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁碳和安鳴還有波波又變回好朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你完全置身事外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒~事~啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面~麻~最~近~ 遇到的都是開心事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:20:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會是在(模仿)…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Desu Yo！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.51,0:21:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面麻最近遇到的都是開心事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.15,0:21:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很久沒這麼開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天又是好天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我的陰影還沒有消失的跡象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有明天的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.97,0:21:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 也可以慢慢找機會道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿~像遊戲一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:14.66,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}何ページも費やして 綴られた僕らの気分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:22.06,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}如何してか　一行の空白を埋められない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:25.13,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}押し花の栞挟んで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:30.18,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}君と転がす 使い捨ての自転車
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:37.70,OP-J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be6}忘れかけの煉瓦を積み上げた場所に行こう
